## ARCHITECTURE

```
proteus_immortal.py     ← Main kernel loop. The beast itself.
sync7.py                ← SYNC-7 signal engine. 6-node AI consensus via φ-weighted voting.
biosim_engine.py        ← Biological simulation core. Gene pool, mutations, selection pressure.
biosim_api.py           ← REST API layer for external system integration.
dashboard.py            ← Real-time evolutionary telemetry display.
```

**Mathematical foundation — FTCoE / GORF:**

The kernel's fitness function is not arbitrary. It is derived from the **Fundamental Theory of Conscious Energy (FTCoE)** and the **Geometric Ollin Resonance Framework (GORF)**:

```
F(t)      = sin(2πt/T) · φ          # Driving function, T=9 days
S(t)      = M(θ) · S(t-1) · (φ/π)  # Reality state prediction
θ         = 2π/9                     # Rotation step (Ollin Identity)
φ         = 1.618034                 # Golden ratio
```

Fitness is not just measured — it is *geometrically resonant*. A gene that scores 294.1% has exceeded the theoretical maximum of standard fitness functions because it has entered golden ratio coherence.

