## QUICK START

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Admin135158/Proteus-Kernel.git
cd Proteus-Kernel
pip install -r requirements.txt
python proteus_immortal.py
```

To run the biosim with dashboard:
```bash
python biosim_engine.py &
python dashboard.py
```

To run SYNC-7 consensus node:
```bash
python sync7.py --nodes all --weight phi
```

